<plot>Hustlas is a dark comedy about strife, loss and yes, even a buff midget. Take a wild ride with the crew of the L.A. News, a motley crew of door-to-door newspaper salesmen whose lives are forever changed during a scorching summer week in Los Angeles. They lie, cheat and brawl with each other to win a cash prize for the most newspapers sold. Things quickly heat up from a friendly comeptition to a full-blown fight. These guys pull just about any stunt to win the contest - even enlisting the help of a buff, hardcore gangster midget? In the end, with sweat and blood on their hands, the L.A. News sales crew learn that in life, there are no winners, just Hustlas.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?250833</url></doc>
